name: "Ar"
description: Before the beginning, there was a breath Antes do que se imaginava, imaginava-se a imaginação Reverbs e reverberations Before the before, after do afer do after Onde estão aqueles acordes? wake ups? chord-melodies? Bossa Nova intuitiva metalinguistic ---  poema, painting and animation by Ronnie "Funilaria Espacial" <IG @funilariaespacial>
